headline: McKesson Corporation Completes Divestiture of Norwegian Operations
summary: IRVING, Texas, January 30, 2026--McKesson Corporation (NYSE: MCK) announced today that it has closed the transaction to sell its retail and distribution businesses in Norway to NorgesGruppen, a privately owned retail group.
